INSTALLATION

Steps:
* Download or clone the repo to where you want to run it.
* Install Node.js, which should come with npm (node package manager).
* 'npm install' in the repo directory will install all dependencies.
* Set PORT number in server.js.
* Set URL and PORT in config.js.
* Set the resolution in config.js.
* Run server.js and open up draw.html, control.html, and render.html in your desired locations.

Any keying application should be configured to load the render.html page.